---
title: Greek-Inspired Tofu Salad with Olives and Feta
description: Is there anything better than a classic, creamy Greek dressing?! Tonight,  Mediterranean-spiced tofu sits atop a Greek-inspired salad with peppers and tomatoes. Briny olives and feta cheese give the perfect salty hit!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R1003_W32_CA_RC153235-3_Main_low-48ff3037.jpg
